as simple as you think.
事情并不像你想象的那么简单。

1127
01:36:22,860 --> 01:36:25,446
<font color="#8cebf2">Sagen Sie Eastgate Ling und Third-ring Ye</font>
Go tell Eastgate Ling
and Third-ring Ye
