1153
01:39:28,963 --> 01:39:32,133
<font color="#8cebf2">bevor es euch hier in den Fingern juckte, Geld zu verdienen.</font>
before you guys here
started itching to make money.
在你们开始渴望赚钱之前。

1154
01:39:32,467 --> 01:39:34,927
<font color="#8cebf2">Ist das Leben in Taipeh wirklich so hart?</font>
