他们就像我们街头帮派一样。

1194
01:42:41,155 --> 01:42:43,324
<font color="#8cebf2">Da war dieser eine Typ.</font>
There was this one guy.
有这么一个人。

1195
01:42:44,158 --> 01:42:46,952
<font color="#8cebf2">Alle dachten, er sei verrückt.</font>
Everyone thought he was crazy.
大家都认为他疯了。

1196
01:42:49,580 --> 01:42:51,123
<font color="#8cebf2">Ich erinnere mich...</font>
I remember...
我记得……

1197
01:42:51,832 --> 01:42:54,627
