and the city was set ablaze.
整座城市被点燃。

1199
01:42:58,422 --> 01:43:01,384
<font color="#8cebf2">Er allein blieb zurück, um Napoleon zu ermorden.</font>
He alone stayed behind
to assassinate Napoleon.
他独自留下来刺杀拿破仑。

1200
01:43:03,260 --> 01:43:06,514
<font color="#8cebf2">Am Ende scheiterte er und wurde gefasst.</font>
In the end,
he failed and was caught.
最后他失败了，并被抓住了。

1201
01:43:09,517 --> 01:43:12,186
<font color="#8cebf2">Krieg und Frieden.</font>
War and Peace.
战争与和平。

1202
01:43:13,020 --> 01:43:16,107
<font color="#8cebf2">Ich habe die Namen aller anderen Romane vergessen.</font>
